\subsection*{Review Questions: Test Your Knowledge}

\begin{marginfigure}[0pt]
\includegraphics[width=0.8\linewidth]{placeholder_questions.png}
\caption{Review questions help you check your understanding and identify areas for further study.}
\label{fig:questions}
